c: 42
v: 48
t: "Bwebaba bagaanye tetukutumanga kuba kalondoozi ku bo, tovunanyizibwa okugyako okutuusa (obubaka). Era mazima ffe bwetukombesa omuntu ku kusaasira okuva gyetuli ku musanyusa, naye bwe batuukwako obuzibu olwebyo emikono gyabwe byegiba gikoze (ng’olwo bakyusa enjogera) anti bulijjo mazima omuntu tasiima"